Built with Llama

This container uses Meta's Llama-Prompt-Guard-2-86M model for prompt
injection and jailbreak detection.

Llama 4 is licensed under the Llama 4 Community License,
Copyright (c) Meta Platforms, Inc. All Rights Reserved.

Model weights are NOT distributed with this container image. They are
downloaded at runtime from HuggingFace upon first startup, subject to
Meta's gated model access requirements and the Llama 4 Community License.

For more information:
- Model: https://huggingface.co/meta-llama/Llama-Prompt-Guard-2-86M
